            </div>
            <div class="service-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-row reveal reveal-delay-3">
            <div class="service-num">04</div>
            <div class="service-name">
                <span class="service-emoji">😁</span> Invisalign
            </div>
            <div class="service-desc">
                Discreet, comfortable clear aligner therapy to straighten your
                smile without wires or brackets.
            </div>
            <div class="service-arrow">→</div>
        </div>
        <div class="service-row reveal reveal-delay-4">
            <div class="service-num">05</div>
